// write a virtual coin toss program. It will randomly tell the user â€œHeadâ€ or â€œTailâ€ you have to use seed value too for cheating

Solution

import random

print("Welcome to the Coin Toss Game!")
seed = int(input("Enter a seed value: "))
random.seed(seed)

if random.randint(0, 1) == 0:
    print("Heads")
else:
    print("Tails")


